      },
      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "A local report doesn’t make it entirely clear, but it sounds like once the dealership employee agreed and probably asked to see his driver’s license, the man pulled out a gun and demanded the keys. The employee handed over the keys and wasn’t injured. Once the man was gone with the car, 911 was called by the dealership.",
